# BrewtifulWorld API
Brewtiful.world is a simple web service that allows developers and beer afficionados to view various beers, breweries, styles and reviews. 
+ [This: Raw API Blueprint](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RJMathis/crafthats/unit_test/apiary.apib)

## Error 
Error Response Code: 500 + ERROR MESSAGE
+ Response 500 (text/plain)
    + Headers
        Error Message: #
    + Body
        error: An internal error occurred: See logs for full stacktrace.
            
## BrewtifulWorld API Root [/]
+ Response 200 (text/plain)
    + Headers
        Link: <https://brewtiful.world/>;rel="self",<https://brewtiful.world/breweries>;rel="breweries",
              <https://brewtiful.world/beers>;rel="beers",<https://brewtiful.world/styles>;rel="styles",
              <https://brewtiful.world/reviews>;rel="reviews",<https://brewtiful.world/brewery>;rel="brewery"
    + Body
        hello world

