## All Breweries [/breweries{?limit,offset}] 
A resource representing all of the beers in the database.

We have added the query URI template parameter's - `limit`. This parameter is
used for limiting the number of results returned by some actions on this
resource. 

We have added the query URI template parameter's - `offset`. This parameter is
used for selecting the page number relative to `limit` of results returned by some actions on this
resource.

#### Retrieve all Breweries [GET]
+ Parameters
    + limit (number, optional) - The maximum number of results to return.
        + Default: `9`
    + offset (number, optional) - The offset number of results to return.
        + Default: `9`

